        <tr>
            <td>
                <span id="ctl00_cph1_LangUserControl_ListView1_ctrl8_Label1"><p>Backblaze (https://www.backblaze.com/) is a popular cloud storage service based in the United States. The service consists of an online backup space where you can save any type of file, using a client software to be installed on the local computer, which takes care of uploading and therefore backing up the data. Backblaze security and reliability features make [&hellip;]</p>
